<content>
    <note id="fs-id1167063684507" class="learning-objectives">
      <label/>
      <title>Section Learning Objectives</title>
      <para id="fs-id1167067202296">By the end of this section, you will be able to do the following:</para>
      <list id="fs-id1167067226853">
        <item>Describe motion in different reference frames</item>
        <item>Define distance and displacement, and distinguish between the two</item>
        <item>Solve problems involving distance and displacement</item>
      </list>
    </note>
      <note id="fs-id1167067048803" class="os-teacher">
        <title>Teacher Support</title>
        <para id="fs-id1167067072798">The learning objectives in this section will help your students master the following standards:</para><list id="fs-id1167063506335"><item>
