<para id="fs-id1164563549296">On an axis in which moving from right to left is positive, what is the displacement and distance of a student who walks 32 m to the right and then 17 m to the left?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164562073661" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
