<para id="fs-id1164566528764">Tiana jogs 1.5 km along a straight path and then turns and jogs 2.4 km in the opposite direction. She then turns back and jogs 0.7 km in the original direction. Let Tianas original direction be the positive direction. What are the displacement and distance she jogged?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164562114390" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>Displacement is 4.6 km,and distance is -0.2 km.</item>
<item>Displacement is -0.2 km, and distance is 4.6 km.</item>
