  </section><section id="fs-id1167063917610" class="summary">
    <title>Section Summary</title>
    <list id="fs-id1167066992275">
      <item>A description of motion depends on the reference frame from which it is described.</item>
      <item>The distance an object moves is the length of the path along which it moves.</item>
      <item>Displacement is the difference in the initial and final positions of an object.</item>

    </list>
