<media id="fs-id1164565114161" alt="A line begins at 0 and extends to the right. 2, 4, 6, 8, 10, and 12 are marked on the line, and it is titled displacement x (m). a green line A extends from 0 to the right. A red line c extends from two to the right, and makes an ess pattern at 10 where it goes back to 8, then reverses direction again and extends to infinity. An orange line D extends from 9 to the left, then reverses direction at 3. A purple line B extends from 12 to the left.">
